components.description:
Toast component for displaying ephemeral notifications.
Typically used via ToastService, not directly.

```typescript
// Use via service
constructor(private toastService: ToastService) {}

showToast() {
  this.toastService.show({
    message: 'Success!',
    variant: 'success'
  });
}
```

